Pat Anderson (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pat_Anderson_(actress) 0 Pat Anderson is an American actress best known for her work in 1970s exploitation films. She played Elaine, an undercover CIA agent who assists the title character in T.N.T. Jackson (1974). Pat_Anderson is an_American_actress best_known for her_work in 1970s_exploitation_films .
